data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch style home nestled on a sprawling 4-acre lot, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and country living. Boasting 1,710 square feet, this home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a charming 13x12 loft area, providing ample room for comfortable living. The 15X27 Detached Garage is another added bonus for parking and storage. Situated in a desirable location, this home offers the perfect balance of privacy and convenience. Enjoy the peacefulness of country living while being just minutes away from Weiss Lake, Pirates Bay Water Park and Little River Canyon!
